-dev`\n   - Set `DEPLOY_ENV=development` in all services\n\n3. Add environment variables:\n   - Stripe keys, Cloudinary credentials, etc. (same as production)\n   - See `DEV_DEPLOYMENT.md` for the complete list\n\nThe frontend configs automatically append `/api` to the API URL if missing, so Render's `fromService` hostname will work correctly.\n\nAll changes are ready. Review the files and let me know if you want any adjustments before deploying.",
